How To Create Custom Kernel Using Speedy Kernel Source For Sony Xperia:
------------------------------------------------
1. Clone Toolchains (or you can use your own toolchains): git clone https://github.com/Divaksh/Toolchains.git
2. In terminal "cd" to source code directory.
3. execute "Make*.sh" to create your boot.img and CWM flashable file
	A. Xperia P => MakeP.sh
	B. Xperia U => MakeU.sh
	C. Xperia Sola => MakeSola.sh
	D. Xperia Go => MakeGo.sh
